{"tid":1795912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動POST跪求人】想知連登係咪真係召集到人","createTime":"2019-12-24T09:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T00:07:31.000Z","uid":134483,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"c5edd0d80c2cea8cef212769e2018ff3f522d8db","tid":1795912,"uid":134483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"容許我入正題前，回顧返呢兩日香港人被打壓的現狀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">12.23 聲援維吾爾族人權集會</span></span>的市民被警察威嚇、暴力驅散<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">12.24 霜夜倒數大遊行</span></span>即使拎到不反，仍受警察諸多限制，被逼取消<br />\n<br />\n香港人　呢刻好需要一場大型活動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集氣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">12.31 除夕夜之路人鏈活動</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗拎不反<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完場自行決定去倒數<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全民皆手足，全民參與<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係</span></span>各位手足，依家我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極度欠缺義工</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾乎<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每個站</span></strong>都唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，好希望大家參與其中，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落</span></span>搞好呢次活動<br />\n話畀全世界聽，香港人有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">打贏極權</span></span>既決心<br />\n<br />\n招義工<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【缺人！缺人！缺人！】</span></span><br />\n出一分力，請Telegram 搵 @<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">GeministandwithHK</span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOj1JvN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOj1JvN.jpg&h=a014f4dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入CHANNEL，主動舉手做義工<br />\n<br />\n荃灣綫︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/TWconnect1231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTWconnect1231&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=55cdc62d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TWconnect1231</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘綫︰觀塘至石硤尾<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MnE0ulTQ4LeieRkZF7f5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMnE0ulTQ4LeieRkZF7f5Qg&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=2c19dfe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MnE0ulTQ4LeieRkZF7f5Qg</a><br />\n<br />\n油尖旺綫︰深水埗至尖沙咀<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/PCl3DRUT8rY0emuYBk9_Qw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FPCl3DRUT8rY0emuYBk9_Qw&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=2c9be60b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/PCl3DRUT8rY0emuYBk9_Qw</a><br />\n<br />\n港島綫︰先逼爆中環至銅鑼灣，再往東西方向延伸<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MF9tYhdUCBeLLsDD522sKA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMF9tYhdUCBeLLsDD522sKA&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=708fab6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MF9tYhdUCBeLLsDD522sKA</a><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳綫︰調景嶺至寶琳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/TKOconnect1231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTKOconnect1231&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0